msgstr ""
"Abra o GRASS Ferramentas e clique duas vezes na categoria: menu: 'Vetor -> "
"Desenvolver mapa -> Geral', em seguida, clique no  mĂłdulo **v.generalize**  "
"para abrir a janela de opĂ§Ă”es."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/grass_integration/grass_integration.rst:727
msgid ""
"Check that the 'ctour_100' vector appears as the :guilabel:`Name of input "
"vector`."
msgstr ""
"Verifique se o vetor 'ctour_100' aparece como :guilabel:`Nome do vetor de "
"entrada`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/grass_integration/grass_integration.rst:733
msgid ""
"You may change the color of the vector to display it clearly on the raster "
"background and to contrast with the original contour lines. You will notice "
"that the new contour lines have smoother corners than the original while "
"staying faithful to the original overall shape."
msgstr ""
"Ă possĂ­vel mudar a cor do vetor para apresentar claramente o fundo matricial"
" e para contrastar com as linhas de contorno originais. VocĂȘ notarĂĄ que as "
"novas linhas de contorno tĂȘm cantos mais suaves do que o original, enquanto "
"permanecer fiel Ă  forma geral de origem."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/grass_integration/grass_integration.rst:744
msgid "GRASS module v.generalize to smooth a vector map"
msgstr "MĂłdulo GRASS v.generalize para suavizar um mapa vetorial"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/grass_integration/grass_integration.rst:746
msgid "**Other uses for r.contour**"
msgstr "**Outros usos para r.contour**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/grass_integration/grass_integration.rst:748
msgid ""
"The procedure described above can be used in other equivalent situations. If"
" you have a raster map of precipitation data, for example, then the same "
"method will be used to create a vector map of isohyetal (constant rainfall) "
