"GRASS Ferramentas, e sob a categoria Raster, clique duas vezes para abrir: "
"menu: 'AnĂĄlise espacial -> AnĂĄlise do Terreno'."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/grass_integration/grass_integration.rst:766
msgid "Then click **r.shaded.relief** to open the module."
msgstr "EntĂŁo, clique **r.shaded.relief** para abrir o mĂłdulo."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/grass_integration/grass_integration.rst:769
msgid ""
"When the process completes, add the hillshade raster to the map. You should "
